<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="pursue-vt">pursue <strong><em>vt</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /pə'sjuː/    美 /pər'suː/  </p>
<p>[正式用语]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>追求；(继续) 从事：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>pursue a goal / an aim</strong> 
追求目标</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I wanted to be a biologist, but I didn’t <strong>pursue</strong> my <strong>dream</strong>. 
我本想成为一名生物学家，但我没有追求自己的梦想。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>追赶；追捕：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>pursue a thief 
追小偷</p></div></div>